The README references `docs/replayer.png`, a screenshot of the egui replayer.

To produce it, first record a session (see the README's `otelma record`), then
replay that recording in the GUI:

    cargo run -p otelma-replay-egui <SESSION_DIR>

This plays the recorded session back with live price/depth plots. Screenshot
the window and save it here as `replayer.png`.

The PNG is not committed in this environment (no display to capture it); drop
the file in and it will appear in the README.
